      "name": "Building a Feature",
      "description": "In this module, you will build a simple Book Manager application using in-memory storage. You will create a List to store books, implement a POST API to add new books, and use GET APIs to retrieve all books or fetch a book by its ID. All the logic will be written inside the Controller, helping you clearly understand how CRUD operations work before moving to layered architecture.",
